                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">General <persName type="from">Lee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Day</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Havana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-01-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 28, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Acting Governor-General Parrado and staff went with me this morning to return
                    visit of Sigsbee. Inspected the <hi rend="italic">Maine</hi>, were entertained
                    and given the appropriate salute. Expressed pleasure at their reception and
                    admiration for the splendid battle ship.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
